<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 12:38:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普指出伊朗袭击推迟后比特币上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/bitcoin-rises-after-trump-says-to-postpone-iran-strikes</link><description>在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示他将对伊朗发电厂和能源基础设施的罢工推迟五天后，比特币与国债和股票期货一起上涨。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV70TN1fQsCU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 11:21:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/bitcoin-rises-after-trump-says-to-postpone-iran-strikes</guid></item><item><title>瑞士私人银行王朝因加密战略冲突而分裂</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/swiss-private-bank-dynasty-splits-over-clashing-views-on-crypto</link><description>瑞士私人银行王朝正因公司未来愿景的不同代际分歧而陷入痛苦之中。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioWHn.dGWqDw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 05:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/swiss-private-bank-dynasty-splits-over-clashing-views-on-crypto</guid></item><item><title>战争紧张局势加剧不确定性，比特币跌至两周低点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/bitcoin-hits-two-week-low-as-war-tensions-fan-uncertainty</link><description>比特币周一在两周低点附近波动，在亚洲早盘交易中下滑，然后在中东紧张局势升级之际反弹至关键支撑位。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iZacU6KS4JyU/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 07:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/bitcoin-hits-two-week-low-as-war-tensions-fan-uncertainty</guid></item><item><title>由于战争担忧影响加密货币市场，比特币跌破 69,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-22/bitcoin-drops-below-69-000-as-war-fears-weigh-on-crypto-markets</link><description>随着美国、以色列和伊朗相互威胁和攻击，比特币和其他加密货币再次下跌。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iBbzxqa3bbmU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 13:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-22/bitcoin-drops-below-69-000-as-war-fears-weigh-on-crypto-markets</guid></item></channel></rss>